prodNameC: 凡立沙 Sm 抗核抗體檢測試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Microplate Strips (coated with a synthetic SmD peptide antigen).
Calibrators (Sm antibody calibrators at concentrations of -3--7-19-40-100 U/ml in PBS containing BSA, 0.095% (w/v) sodium azide, detergent and human serum).
Positive Control (containing BSA, 0.095% (w/v) sodium azide, detergent and human serum).
Negative Control (containing BSA, 0.095% (w/v) sodium azide, detergent and human serum). 
Wash Buffer Concentrate (20x PBS concentrate containing 0.095% (w/v) sodium azide and detergent).
Sample Diluent (PBS containing BSA, 0.095% (w/v) sodium azide and detergent). 
IgG HRP Conjugate (anti-human IgG HRP conjugate).
Substrate TMB (3, 3’, 5, 5’Tetramethylbenzidine).
Stop Solution (0.5M H2SO4).
applicantName: 台灣法迪亞股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區建國北路2段147號8樓之1
efficacy: 定性及半定量測定人體血清或血漿中的Sm抗體。
